(school bell ringing)

02:44.932 --> 02:47.366
I ran into blaine and
karofsky last night.

02:47.368 --> 02:49.701
Then i spent the rest of
the night having a fantasy

02:49.703 --> 02:51.436
About singing "it's too
late" all over town.

02:51.438 --> 02:52.437
