02:52.439 --> 02:54.339
Hey.

02:54.341 --> 02:57.209
Why don't we use carole king's
seminal break-up album<i> tapestry</i>

02:57.211 --> 02:58.610
As this week's lesson?

02:58.612 --> 02:59.845
Yeah, it's brilliant,
but, i mean,

02:59.847 --> 03:01.346
It's sort of a downer,
don't you think?

03:01.348 --> 03:02.814
If we're gonna do
a break-up album,

03:02.816 --> 03:04.816
