<i>jagged little pill,</i>

03:04.818 --> 03:06.985
'cause it's modern
and edgy and angry.

03:06.987 --> 03:08.487
And isn't that
the kind of energy

03:08.489 --> 03:10.055
That we want these
new kids expressing?

03:10.057 --> 03:12.024
