obsessed with rap and journey,

03:16.163 --> 03:17.896
But at least we
all left glee club

03:17.898 --> 03:19.865
With a better understanding
and appreciation

03:19.867 --> 03:21.833
Of all kinds of music.
You know?

03:21.835 --> 03:24.803
It's our job to educate as well
as win competitions, you know?

03:24.805 --> 03:26.338
Maybe it was easier
for mr. Shue

03:26.340 --> 03:28.307
'cause he didn't have
a partner to answer to.

03:28.309 --> 03:29.641
I...

03:29.643 --> 03:31.043
I'm just, you know,
getting worried

03:31.045 --> 03:32.477
About this
co-teaching thing.

03:32.479 --> 03:34.379
