to start hating each other.

03:34.381 --> 03:36.348
Wait, why don't we
do both albums?

03:36.350 --> 03:38.350
We'll make it
a mash-up week.

03:38.352 --> 03:40.986
Think about it, uh,<i> jagged</i>
<i>little pill</i> and<i> tapestry.</i>

03:40.988 --> 03:43.989
Two great albums written by
great singer-songwriters.

03:43.991 --> 03:45.524
That's brilliant because
then we can educate them

03:45.526 --> 03:47.159
And get them fired up
at the same time.

03:47.161 --> 03:49.094
We're so good!
Yes, on fire,
rachel, fire!

03:49.096 --> 03:50.529
You and me, together.

03:50.531 --> 03:52.731
(school bell ringing)

03:53.534 --> 03:54.900
Sorry i'm late.

03:54.902 --> 03:57.769
I think i got some
bad sushi last night.

03:57.771 --> 04:01.607
I seriously did not get
off the pot until about...

04:01.609 --> 04:04.343
15 minutes ago.

04:04.345 --> 04:05.911
So, uh, how was practice?

04:05.913 --> 04:07.579
Uh, you know, amazing, yeah.

04:07.581 --> 04:09.414
Only two guys passed out
from dehydration.

04:09.416 --> 04:11.683
Well, you can't
criticize the results.

04:11.685 --> 04:12.851
The guys love you.

04:12.853 --> 04:15.354
They work hard for you.

04:15.356 --> 04:18.624
Like i say, miracle whip
works fine on a burger, but...

04:18.626 --> 04:20.726
Both: You can't use it
to skin a cat.

04:20.728 --> 04:22.060
Thanks, coach, yeah.

04:22.062 --> 04:23.795
Um, no, i'm having
the time of my life here.

04:23.797 --> 04:26.265
I mean, if you asked me what
my dream was, like, right now,

04:26.267 --> 04:28.367
Besides like, having one of
those, like, giant talking m&m's

04:28.369 --> 04:29.601
And, uh, making it my pet...

04:29.603 --> 04:30.969
(chuckles)
it would probably be

04:30.971 --> 04:33.038
To take over your job
when you retire.

04:33.040 --> 04:34.273
It's, like, my ultimate fantasy.

04:34.275 --> 04:35.974
You could do it, too.

04:35.976 --> 04:38.543
You've got the gift, sam.
That's why i've been

04:38.545 --> 04:41.213
Entrusting you in running
practice couple days a week.

04:41.215 --> 04:42.381
Oh, hey, um...

04:42.383 --> 04:43.782
Are you, uh...

04:43.784 --> 04:45.117
Are you... Are you okay?

04:45.119 --> 04:46.918
What?
I-i mean,
like i said,

04:46.920 --> 04:49.554
I-i'm super grateful, um...
But, frankly,

04:49.556 --> 04:51.556
Everybody thinks it's
kind of suspicious for you

04:51.558 --> 04:53.158
To skip out of practice at all.

04:53.160 --> 04:54.993
Well, you tell 'em to mind
their own damn business!

04:54.995 --> 04:56.995
Whoa, uh, nobody's accusing you
of anything.

04:56.997 --> 04:58.830
I... And definitely not me.

04:58.832 --> 05:00.999
Honestly, i'm, you know,
i'm just...

05:01.001 --> 05:02.100
I'm worried about you.

05:02.102 --> 05:04.503
It-it's my knee.

05:04.505 --> 05:06.838
Looks like i'm gonna have
to have it replaced again.

05:06.840 --> 05:08.974
And i'll probably have to
take off a couple weeks.

05:08.976 --> 05:10.942
Is that all?
God, okay, i was worried

05:10.944 --> 05:12.477
It was something more serious.
I mean, like...

05:12.479 --> 05:13.945
Well, that explains
the extra leg hair.

05:13.947 --> 05:15.347
It must hurt to shave.

05:15.349 --> 05:17.582
I've been trying to
keep it hush-hush.

05:17.584 --> 05:19.985
You know, i feel like
the-the team needs to see me

05:19.987 --> 05:21.186
As, like, iron shannon,

05:21.188 --> 05:23.689
You know, this
invincible titan.

05:23.691 --> 05:25.390
Hey, coach... Es.

05:27.027 --> 05:29.795
Uh... You got a second to talk
about the starters for friday?

05:29.797 --> 05:32.264
I'll post it friday
morning, same as always.

05:32.266 --> 05:33.332
I want a shot
at quarterback.

05:33.334 --> 05:34.766
You're my best receiver.

05:34.768 --> 05:36.601
I've been taking snaps
in practice for weeks.

05:36.603 --> 05:37.869
I came in
the last four minutes

05:37.871 --> 05:39.037
Of the game against central

05:39.039 --> 05:40.205
And threw for four first downs.

05:40.207 --> 05:42.374
And no touchdowns.

05:42.376 --> 05:43.842
And you know why?

05:43.844 --> 05:45.644
Because you didn't have you
to throw to.

05:45.646 --> 05:47.979
I told you
this 50 times.

05:47.981 --> 05:50.015
You take fred flintstone
off the brontosaurus,

05:50.017 --> 05:53.218
All he is, is wilma with
a set of man-plumbs.

05:53.220 --> 05:54.586
Conversation over.

05:57.624 --> 06:00.025
Look, dude, man.
Tough break, buddy, okay?

06:00.027 --> 06:02.494
I think you're like a majestic
knight riding a horse.

06:02.496 --> 06:05.564
If it were up to me,
i'd give you a shot.

06:07.701 --> 06:09.334
(school bell ringing)

06:09.336 --> 06:11.370
Okay, why don't i start it
with the title,

06:11.372 --> 06:13.171
